The line `simp only [Sequent.flip, Olf.flip, Option.map_some, Sum.swap_inl, Tableau.flip, ...] at *` will be changed to `simp [Sequent.isLoaded] at *`. This change will be applied to the first case (`loc`) of `tab`.

